short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: This extension allows direct proxy access and switching for Proksee.co users

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
To enable direct access to proxies found on Proksee.co price discovery service , please download this extension - Once a ProkseeLink is clicked your browser will automatically be redirected to the relevant proxy and the link you searched will be opened. When changing back to another browsing window/tab, direct browsing settings will automatically be applied.

Note: Please enable incognito mode access for this extension to work properly
